{"tid":1131729,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤：「我本身好唔受歡迎，男又好女又好！」","createTime":"2019-04-30T00:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T04:44:02.000Z","uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"626cb52061aead6768c886c263c084b1965a47a0","tid":1131729,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190417/s00009/a7f4c374ddb42b49a90d5971b721778b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190417%2Fs00009%2Fa7f4c374ddb42b49a90d5971b721778b.jpg&h=8099b577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤和師弟楊天宇前晚出席代言戶日本健膚品牌UL．OS活動，席間兩人即場度胸肌，最後由43吋胸肌的阿澤鬥贏36吋的楊天宇，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>阿澤笑言：「我大過佢，不過佢長過我，話佢隻腳呀！」</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主持提及阿澤喜歡下廚，他<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>即抵死說：「做廚房佬成日偷食，但用濕紙巾抹嘴就大步檻過。」</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當播出兩人的廣告片時，現場有人要求阿澤即場Rap，阿澤即謂：「本來有人9月開騷（指許志安紅館騷） ，如果我攞到個期，幾多錢我都畀。」引得全場爆笑！<br />\n<br />\n提到見到身旁的師弟高大又靚仔會否好羨慕？阿澤笑謂：「咁又唔會，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我有嘅嘢佢又冇嘅，不過我啲長處都係收埋好啲。」</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問到他會否惹來不少飛來蜢？他直言：「<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我本身好唔受歡迎，男又好女又好</span></span></strong>，所以我從來都唔擔心呢啲問題，所以老婆一向都好放心，因為我生得醜，所以冇呢啲煩憂。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔得啦澤囝實在太好笑 我笑到好辛苦呀！<br />\n紅字為笑點👆👆👆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.itw01.com/images/2018/04/14/09/4031_k12tiT_VOIGQEJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.itw01.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F09%2F4031_k12tiT_VOIGQEJ.jpg&h=6c2f55e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打我留意左你好耐<br />\n你真係好幽默<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默既人 但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍<br />\n錯 應該係100倍先岩<br />\n估唔到我係呢個post竟然見識到你既威力<br />\n我真係笑到爆左肚 依家一路打字一路撿返d腸呀內臟呀腎呀<br />\n塞返落個肚到<br />\n你有冇諗過<del>未來幾個</del><strong>九</strong>月去紅館開棟篤笑?"},{"pid":"6d78d00cb734d27a24beace258530d2e8266d98c","tid":1131729,"uid":121060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:24:04.000Z","msg":"又係呢條垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356b060295b26cc310b21485e96c58545bc78b48","tid":1131729,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d78d00cb734d27a24beace258530d2e8266d98c","tid":1131729,"uid":121060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:24:04.000Z","msg":"又係呢條垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"邊個反牙怯，邊個就係五毛！"},{"pid":"43fde3fbb084f207d3d5585b8f102f9b2d6e37bc","tid":1131729,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed488ce944d4f726653cdfde7d4497e7c3f61e1","tid":1131729,"uid":59920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤代言戶日本健膚品牌UL．OS活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}